# 🌍 Tour Management System

A full-stack **Tour Management System** built using **Java, JSP, Servlets, JDBC, and PostgreSQL**. The application allows users to explore tour packages, register and log in securely, book tours, manage bookings, and enjoy a modern responsive user interface.

---

## 📌 Overview

The Tour Management System is designed to simplify the process of discovering and booking travel packages. It follows the **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** architecture and demonstrates the implementation of Java Web Technologies with database integration.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 User Registration & Login
- 🔑 Forgot Password & Password Reset
- 🏞 Browse Available Tours
- 🔍 Search Tours
- 📅 Book Tour Packages
- 📋 View My Bookings
- ❌ Cancel Bookings
- 💻 Responsive Glassmorphism UI
- 🗄 PostgreSQL Database Integration
- 🔒 Session-Based Authentication

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

| Category | Technologies |
|----------|--------------|
| Language | Java |
| Backend | JSP, Servlets, JDBC |
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript |
| Database | PostgreSQL |
| Build Tool | Maven |
| Server | Apache Tomcat |
| IDE | Eclipse IDE |

---

## 🏗 Project Architecture

The application follows the **MVC Architecture**.

```
Presentation Layer
│
├── JSP
├── HTML
├── CSS
└── JavaScript
        │
        ▼
Controller Layer
│
└── Java Servlets
        │
        ▼
Business Logic
│
└── DAO Classes
        │
        ▼
Database
│
└── PostgreSQL
```

