## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Java JDK 17+
- Apache Tomcat 10+
- PostgreSQL
- Maven
- Eclipse IDE

### Installation

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/pratheekr7777-dotcom/Tour-Management-System.git
```

2. Import the project into Eclipse as a Maven project.

3. Configure PostgreSQL database credentials.

4. Run the SQL script to create the required tables.

5. Deploy the project on Apache Tomcat.

6. Open:

```
http://localhost:8080/tour_management_system
```

